{"tid":611687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【琴日係地獄老師 香港首播20週年】","createTime":"2018-03-31T09:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T10:55:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c73ff85c6538674e2350b15ebf3f93887c077e","tid":611687,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T09:25:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/172514_e0c6e9d23b45ba7500b0920fa296e961.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F172514_e0c6e9d23b45ba7500b0920fa296e961.png&h=ce5b401d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;呢個世界上,有啲黑暗嘅物體,用我哋肉眼係睇唔到嘅,而佢哋一有機會,就會張牙舞爪襲擊你哋,但係有個人,為咗保護你哋免受呢啲妖魔鬼怪侵害,同埋消滅呢啲邪惡黑暗嘅物體,由地獄深處嚟到呢度,佢就係正義嘅使者&mdash;&mdash;地獄老師！&rdquo;（本港台版開場白）<br />\n<br />\n呢套係90年代嘅卡通,日文原名叫 「地獄先生ぬ～べ～」, 香港當年引進譯做「地獄老師」，而台灣則譯成「靈異教師神眉」<br />\n<br />\n「地獄老師」係一套圍繞日本著名靈異鬼故以及日本傳說為中心嘅作品.電視方面,90年代尾在亞視選擇係年青人最喜歡嘅深夜時段播放,頗受歡迎,尤其係主題曲,相當熱血.至於影碟方面,「愛子動畫」亦推出過一套自家配音版."},{"pid":"e7ca81dee3e9bce6805810b384928790b2bb7f27","tid":611687,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2125f54c06424f7e6fc54779379de9c21e47e2","tid":611687,"uid":64093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"班5p仔識hi 咩"},{"pid":"d8db6bd0b0c6febd4511de4343d0dcd9eee9efab","tid":611687,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"用鉛筆芯插入擦膠度吊住佢可以唔知驅鬼定見鬼"},{"pid":"fe9dba3e4666d4172bfb9bd1077ba3510d473401","tid":611687,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b495358e00effbb250abfd6b260793b24798bf8","tid":611687,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a